An evil woman has committed one the most abominable act of all times after slitting the throats of her co-wife&#8217;s twins in one the most gruesome murder ever.The woman who is yet to be identified, reportedly abandoned the children in the pool of their blood with the knife right beside them before she attempted to abscond, and was arrested and handcuffed before succeeding in her escape moves.As at the time of filing this report, the reason for the wicked and devilish act by the woman is still yet unknown. According to a shocking report posted on facebook by Precious Eze, a tragic incident played out at the weekend in Katsina State after a woman allegedly slit the throats of her co-wife s twins at the Batagarawa Local Government Area of the state.Source : iMzansi!&nbsp;